<PartnerLayout
    title="Carrier"
    highlightedText="Network"
    description="Partner with HaulCo and take your moving business to the next level with our technology and volume."
    summaryTitle="Grow Your Fleet with HaulCo"
    summaryText="We're looking for professional, reliable carriers to join our elite network. By partnering with HaulCo, you gain access to a massive pool of customers, advanced logistics tools, and a support team dedicated to your success. We handle the sales and technology, so you can focus on what you do best: moving."
    summaryImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519003722824-194d4455a60c?q=80&w=2075&auto=format&fit=crop"
    benefits={benefits}
    ctaTitle="Ready to join our network?"
